@startuml
title Formulaire de contact

actor Visiteur as User
participant Frontend as Front
participant API as API
database BaseDeDonnees as BD

== Saisie ==
User -> Front: Accéder à\n"Me contacter"
Front --> User: Formulaire (nom, email, message)

User -> Front: Remplir et soumettre
Front -> API: POST /api/contact
note right: Validation coté serveur\n(sanitize, anti-spam)

alt validation OK
  API -> BD: INSERT Contact
  note right: est_lu = false
  BD --> API: Message enregistré
  API -> BD: Notifier propriétaire
  API --> Front: Message envoyé
  Front --> User: Confirmation + message\nde remerciement
else erreur
  API --> Front: Erreur validation
  Front --> User: Corriger le formulaire
end

@enduml
